{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"FederatedCredential","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential_Management_API\">Credential Management API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/protocol\"><code>protocol</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/provider\"><code>provider</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu Credential Management API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CredentialsContainer\"><code>CredentialsContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PasswordCredential\"><code>PasswordCredential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PublicKeyCredential\"><code>PublicKeyCredential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Dies ist eine experimentelle Technologie</strong><br>Da diese Technologie noch nicht definitiv implementiert wurde, sollte die <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browserkompatibilität</a> beachtet werden. Es ist auch möglich, dass die Syntax in einer späteren Spezifikation noch geändert wird.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<strong><code>FederatedCredential</code></strong>&nbsp;Schnittstelle der&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential_Management_API\">Credential Management API</a>&nbsp;stellt Informationen über Zugangsdaten eines Anbieters föderierter Identitäten bereit. Ein Anbieter föderierter Identitäten ist ein Gebilde, dem eine Webseite vertraut, eine Nutzerin korrekt zu identifizieren und eine API für diesen Zweck bereit stellt.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://openid.net/developers/specs/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">OpenID Connect</a>&nbsp;ist ein Beispiel für ein Framework für Anbieter föderierter Identitäten.</p>\n\n<p>In Brwosern, die dies unterstützen, kann eine Instanz dieser Schnittstelle in der&nbsp;<code>credential</code> Funktions des&nbsp;<code>init</code> Objekt für globales <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/fetch\"><code>fetch</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> mitgegeben werden.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"federatedcredential_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/FederatedCredential\"><code>FederatedCredential()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Erstellt ein neues&nbsp;<code>FederatedCredential</code> Objekt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Erbt Eigenschaften von seinem Vorfahren, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"federatedcredential.provider_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FederatedCredential/provider\"><code>FederatedCredential.provider</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;<span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Gibt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a> zurück, der den Anbieter föderierter Identitäten eines Satzes von Zugangsdaten enthält.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event-handler","title":"Event-Handler","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Keine.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Keine.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> cred <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FederatedCredential</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">provider</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://account.google.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">iconURL</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> iconUrl\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Store it</span>\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>credentials<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">store</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>cred<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Mach etwas anderes.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webappsec-credential-management/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" t